              <item>
               <widget class="QLabel" name="label_4">
                <property name="text">
                 <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600; color:#ffff7f;&quot;&gt;For 48 years no other gym has been responsible for more life-&lt;br/&gt;changing transformations and fitness achievements than&lt;br/&gt;FAT HATER GYM. From a small gym in Ghasrodasht street, Shiraz to&lt;br/&gt;the most well-known traditional fitness company in the world &lt;br/&gt;spanning 6 continents.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
