              <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600; color:#ffff7f;&quot;&gt;Built on discipline, hard work, and respect for the sport, we have stayed&lt;br/&gt;- true to the classic spirit of bodybuilding while constantly evolving&lt;br/&gt; with the times. &lt;br/&gt;Today, FAT HATER GYM is more than a name—it’s a community &lt;br/&gt;where beginners become athletes, goals become routines, and&lt;br/&gt;routines become lifestyles. &lt;br/&gt;Step inside and you’ll feel it: &lt;br/&gt;the energy, the history, and the &lt;br/&gt;standards that push every member to be stronger than yesterday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
